---
import Logo from "../../assets/logos/LogoTriasoUs.png";
---
<div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-center items-stretch font-bold text-white bg-blueMain px-8 lg:px-32 relative gap-3 md:gap-10 py-10">
    <div class="p-6 m-4 bg-grisT rounded-2xl h-full z-10">
        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">On-Demand Asphalt Production</h2><br>
        <p class="text-grisSubP">
            Cold mix plants offer the flexibility to produce aggregate mix on-site as needed, reducing dependence
             on external suppliers. This minimizes delays and allows the mix to be prepared and applied immediately
              â€” an advantage for remote locations and emergency repair projects.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 m-4 bg-grisT rounded-2xl h-full z-10">
        <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">Low Operating Costs</h2><br>
        <p class="text-grisSubP">
            Without burners or thermal oil systems, cold mix plants significantly reduced fuel consumption and maintenance
             expenses. Their simple mechanical design minimizes downtime and supports long-term operational  efficiency
              for both municipalities and contractors.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-0">
        <img src={Logo.src} alt="">
    </div>
</div>